thrust follows maxima to the base

EmprzAnastazia@... wrote:Maxima glanced between Thrust & the others. "Perhaps we should return to base, there everything will be explained." 

Once again looking at them all, "I pressume you all can still fly. If not, find a way to. Move out, quickly."

Maxima then took to the air. Yes, she was in a hurry to return to base, & it wasn't totally about Hydras, but something that bothered her internally. She felt that she had to get them to base a quickly as possible.
